  "content": "<blockquote data-pid=\"XgdXhCLp\">所谓建议，往往是我们已然知晓答案，却又不愿面对时所求之物。 (<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erica_Jong\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Erica Jong</a>)</blockquote><p data-pid=\"4_KDsmKn\">此处汇集了本人关于数学学术生涯各方面问题的一些建议，大致按照建议与职业生涯阶段的关联性进行了排列（当然，部分建议也适用于多个阶段）。</p><p data-pid=\"xfG_mn7G\"><b>免责声明</b>：此处的建议本质上非常宽泛；我并不奢望能提供任何解决所有职业难题的「银弹」。在做出任何重要的职业决定之前，你无疑需要评估诸多特定于自身情况的因素、背景和需求，并运用充分的常识。我尤其建议，若你有导师，务必<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/talk-to-your-advisor/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">与你的导师商议此类决定</a>，因为他/她熟悉你的情况，并且很可能能够提供中肯的建议。此外，需要明确的是，此处大部分建议主要针对数学领域的学术生涯；当然，除此以外还有许多其他职业选择，但我对那些替代路径并无特别专业的见解可供分享。</p><ul><li data-pid=\"RaFSC9Sc\"> 小学阶段<br/> </li><ul><li data-pid=\"AMgnBo0b\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/advice-on-gifted-education/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">关于天才教育的建议</a><sup data-text=\"关于天才教育的建议\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1952323438195762299\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>。 <br/></li></ul><li data-pid=\"AJkrQlZ7\"> 中学阶段<br/> </li><ul><li data-pid=\"pQOmotYq\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/advice-on-mathematics-competitions/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">关于数学竞赛的建议</a>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"o6cX8sZU\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/which-universities-should-one-apply-to/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">应该申请哪些大学？</a><br/> </li></ul><li data-pid=\"Bi7FtEC1\"> 本科阶段<br/> </li><ul><li data-pid=\"ZUk6gHTN\"> 如何才能更擅长<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/solving-mathematical-problems/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">解决数学问题</a><sup data-text=\"解决数学问题\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1915697792904598747\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup>？请注意，<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/theres-more-to-mathematics-than-grades-and-exams-and-methods/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">数学的意义远不止分数、考试和方法</a><sup data-text=\"数学不只是成绩、考试，和刷题套路\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1932026929369814800\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup>；同时，<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/theres-more-to-mathematics-than-rigour-and-proofs/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">数学的内涵也远不止严谨与证明</a>。同样重要的是，要<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/on-the-importance-of-partial-progress/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">珍视在解决问题过程中取得的阶段性进展，将其视为通往完整解决方案的关键基石</a>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"L4DuxhHA\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/don%25E2%2580%2599t-base-career-decisions-on-glamour-or-fame/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">切勿仅凭光环或名望做职业决定</a>。但你应该<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/study-at-different-places/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">尝试在不同的地方求学</a>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"AUdatg-o\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/does-one-have-to-be-a-genius-to-do-maths/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">在数学上取得成功一定要是天才吗？</a><sup data-text=\"一定要是天才才能做数学吗？\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1920412032219477942\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"4\">[4]</sup><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"KBt0j7Ry\"> 我于 2022 年在哈维穆德学院毕业典礼上的演讲（<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3DjE-vY5-3zhU%26t%3D1768s\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">视频</a>）。<br/> </li></ul><li data-pid=\"DRyVXHaY\"> 研究生阶段<br/> </li><ul><li data-pid=\"OUlS3qd6\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/work-hard/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">努力工作</a><sup data-text=\"努力工作\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1929112218194141263\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"5\">[5]</sup>和<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/be-professional-in-your-work/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">以专业的态度工作</a>至关重要。但同时，<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/enjoy-your-work/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">享受你的工作</a><sup data-text=\"享受你的工作\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1924787760381826535\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"6\">[6]</sup>也同样重要。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"e9duOKy-\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/think-ahead/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">向前看</a>以明晰前进之路；<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/ask-yourself-dumb-questions-and-answer-them/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">向自己提出看似愚笨的问题</a><sup data-text=\"不妨问自己一些傻问题——并尝试解答它们！\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1913642751054046402\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"7\">[7]</sup>以洞察过往基础。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"9wAuGWXc\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/attend-talks-and-conferences-even-those-not-directly-related-to-your-work/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">参加学术报告和会议，即便是那些与你本人工作不直接相关的</a>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"4i539Sov\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/talk-to-your-advisor/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">与你的导师交流</a>，并且要<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/take-the-initiative/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">主动交流</a>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"uQTZ3bko\"> 切勿<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/dont-prematurely-obsess-on-a-single-big-problem-or-big-theory/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">过早沉溺于单一的「重大难题」或「宏大理论」</a>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"CaOm2rdj\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/write-down-what-youve-done/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">记录下你所做的工作</a>，并<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/make-your-work-available/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">将你的成果公之于众</a>。关于这一点，我有一些<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">关于如何撰写和提交论文的建议</a>。<br/> </li></ul><li data-pid=\"YWj7Aiyi\"> 「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.ams.org/journals/notices/202007/rnoti-p1007.pdf\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">一次惊险：一次几近失败如何推动我走向成功</a>」，T. Tao，《美国数学会会刊·通告》（<i>Notices of the American Mathematical Society</i>），2020 年 8 月。最初发表于「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.ams.org/about-us/LivingProof.pdf\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">活生生的证明：数学旅程中的坚韧故事</a>」，美国数学会，2019 年。编辑：Allison Henrich、Emille Lawrence、Matthew Pons、David Taylor。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"b1d0HZ9s\"> 博士后阶段<br/> </li><ul><li data-pid=\"7DilA5fB\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/learn-and-relearn-your-field/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">学习并时常温习你的领域</a><sup data-text=\"学习并时常温习你的领域\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1939620723808244220\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"8\">[8]</sup>，但<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/dont-be-afraid-to-learn-things-outside-your-field/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">不要害怕学习你领域之外的知识</a>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"kGM45WPL\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/learn-the-limitations-of-your-tools/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">了解你工具的局限性</a><sup data-text=\"认识到你所用工具的局限\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1935759986283254667\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"9\">[9]</sup>，但也要<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/learn-the-power-of-other-mathematicians-tools/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">学习其他数学家工具的强大之处</a>。尤其重要的是，你应该<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/continually-aim-just-beyond-your-current-range/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">持续挑战略高于你当前能力范围的目标</a><sup data-text=\"持续挑战能力边界\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1939621056060045178\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"10\">[10]</sup>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"zo7KoD8K\"> 在你的研究中，既要<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/be-flexible/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">灵活变通</a><sup data-text=\"保持灵活性\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1945781278394787244\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"11\">[11]</sup>也要<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/be-patient/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">保持耐心</a><sup data-text=\"保持耐心\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1926976019300094709\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"12\">[12]</sup>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"PYYCDP9i\"> 若有机会，你绝对应该出行并展示你的研究成果。但务必<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/be-considerate-of-your-audience/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">体谅你的听众</a>；学术报告<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/talks-are-not-the-same-as-papers/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">与论文有所不同</a>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"h7cBC9RQ\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/be-sceptical-of-your-own-work/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">对你自己的工作保持审慎的态度</a>，并且不要害怕<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/use-the-wastebasket/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">使用废纸篓</a><sup data-text=\"善用废纸篓\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1943602163445133837\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"13\">[13]</sup>。<br/> </li></ul></ul><p data-pid=\"NMvJOrV4\">我亦在（缓慢地）从研究数学家的视角，整理我对时间管理的思考。</p><ul><li data-pid=\"x1rSRMqJ\"> 这里有一些关于此主题的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/2008/08/07/on-time-management/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">一般性想法</a><sup data-text=\"陶哲轩论时间管理\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1917527213198279519\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"14\">[14]</sup>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"VKwR3D1z\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/batch-low-intensity-tasks-together/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">将低强度的任务集中处理</a>，以利用规模效应并减少干扰。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"1LQSDcqF\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/2017/07/07/what-are-some-useful-but-little-known-features-of-the-tools-used-in-professional-mathematics/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">专业数学家所用工具有哪些实用却鲜为人知的功能？</a><br/> </li></ul><p data-pid=\"5GbKYRsN\">更多建议：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"YsxZ_F2z\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//math.ucr.edu/home/baez/advice.html\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">John Baez 的职业建议页面</a>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"rnLpuuQZ\"> Po Bronson 关于<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//nymag.com/news/features/27840/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">天赋与努力相对重要性的文章</a>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"6Y8-NJj2\"> Catherine Cannizzo 的「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//sites.google.com/view/ccannizzo/postdoc-apps\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">博士后申请指南</a>」。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"3ayj31zx\"> Fan Chung 给<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.math.ucsd.edu/~fan/teach/gradpol.html\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">研究生的建议</a>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"2kAOYrgl\"> Lance Fortnow 的「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//weblog.fortnow.com/2007/02/graduate-student-guide.html\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">研究生指南</a>」。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"Y56_9sKg\"> Oded Goldreich 的「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wisdom.weizmann.ac.il/~oded/on-duties.html\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">论我们作为科学家的职责</a>」。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"O0-sqSSf\"> Richard Hamming 的「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.mccurley.org/advice/hamming_advice.html\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">灵光一闪：在你所做的一切中力求卓越</a>」。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"sc_BZfBX\"> Matt Might 的「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//matt.might.net/articles/phd-school-in-pictures/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">图解博士之路</a>」。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"CAfBkJ-d\"> Gian-Carlo Rota 的「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.ams.org/notices/199701/comm-rota.pdf\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">我希望当初有人教我的十堂课</a>」。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"0L4ym5Vu\"> J. Michael Steele 的「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www-stat.wharton.upenn.edu/~steele/Rants/AdviceGS.html\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">给统计学研究生的建议</a>」。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"pcaw4E1w\"> Ian Stewart 的「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.amazon.com/Letters-Young-Mathematician-Art-Mentoring/dp/0465082319/sr%3D8-1/qid%3D1170790056/ref%3Dpd_bbs_1/002-2734562-8194451%3Fie%3DUTF8%26s%3Dbooks\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">给青年数学家的信</a>」。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"6Qha8G_v\"> Ravi Vakil 的「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//math.stanford.edu/~vakil/potentialstudents.html\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">写给潜在的学生们</a>」。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"ITDnXf8Y\"> Remy van Dobben de Bruyn 的「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//remy%2520van%2520dobben%2520de%2520bruyn/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">博士后申请时间规划</a>」。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"sUeNfw4Q\"> Lauren William 的「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//math.berkeley.edu/~katrin/slides/Williams-FindingJob.pdf\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">如何在数学领域找到博士后职位</a>」。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"hqhFfgsk\"> 《<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//press.princeton.edu/titles/8350.html\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">普林斯顿数学指南</a>》中<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//press.princeton.edu/chapters/gowers/gowers_VIII_6.pdf\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">「给年轻数学家的建议」</a>一节，撰稿人包括 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Atiyah\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Michael Atiyah 爵士</a>、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%25C3%25A9la_Bollob%25C3%25A1s\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Béla Bollobás</a>、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alain_Connes\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Alain Connes</a>、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dusa_McDuff\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Dusa McDuff</a> 和 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Sarnak\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Peter Sarnak</a>。<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"gtKqI0rE\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.ams.org/cgi-bin/notices/nxgnotices.pl%3Ffm%3Dgen%26cnt%3Dcareer\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《美国数学会通告》中的早期职业生涯文章</a><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"No4eNSIo\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//mathgradblog.williams.edu/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">美国数学会研究生博客</a><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"1n3JIGZe\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//math.stackexchange.com/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Mathematics Stack Exchange</a> 网站上有<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//math.stackexchange.com/questions/tagged/career-development%3Fsort%3Dvotes%26pagesize%3D15\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">许多关于职业发展的问题与解答</a>（你也可以在该网站上提出尚未被提出的其他问题）。<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//mathoverflow.net/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">MathOverflow</a> 网站类似地也有<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//mathoverflow.net/questions/tagged%3Ftagnames%3Dcareer%26sort%3Dvotes%26pagesize%3D15\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">关于职业发展的问题与解答</a>。最后，<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//academia.stackexchange.com/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Academia Stack Exchange</a> 网站上有大量关于所有学术事务（包括职业问题）的问题与解答。</li></ul><hr/><blockquote data-pid=\"7TvEH3sh\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 gemini-2.5-pro，校对 <span class=\"nolink\">bstiat</span><br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Career advice | What&#39;s new</a></blockquote>",
